('577d1ead-d3b9-44f2-a78c-53c9d627e198', '5612643644b65', 'Mentorship for a refugee or a small family', 'I would like to offer a mentorship for a single refugee or a small family. We could meet weekly or every second week at the weekend. Meeting, talking, visiting museums or other spots in the city, small tours in the surrounding of Dresden.\r\n\r\nAbout myself: I work in medical physics research in Dresden. I am 34 years old, male, and live together with my husband. Hence there would be empathy and sensibility for a gay refugee. Of cause, we would welcome every refugee independent of sexual orientation, religion and so on.', 'richter.chr@gmail.com', '', '', '+491741772564', 3, 'de', 'Christian Richter', '', '', 'logo', NULL, 'englisch', '2015-10-05 13:51:18', '2015-10-21 19:52:57', 1, 1, 'df402493-f467-4472-8b98-9038d2ac967e', 0, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL),
